			subtitle: "The Slimeball and the Ingot will be required to advance further. While you can just infuse some Aluminum with Liquid Pink Slime to obtain the Ingot, the Slimeball will be more difficult to obtain. Pink Slimeballs have to be grown using seeds from Mystical Agriculture"
